<div class="container">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to LungCancerDetect!</h1>
        <p>
            LungCancerDetect is a cutting-edge website that leverages machine learning and CRISPR technology to detect and treat lung cancer.
        </p>
